00:22:59.550 --> 00:23:03.560
do it in one syllable--
OK, so just ignore

00:23:03.560 --> 00:23:04.790
my multi-syllabic words.

00:23:04.790 --> 00:23:07.090
But anyway, he
says, I have managed

00:23:07.090 --> 00:23:15.100
to write an article with all
words with just one syllable,

00:23:15.100 --> 00:23:20.847
except for this last syllable--
OK, I lost it-- sorry.

00:23:20.847 --> 00:23:22.430
But anyway, the last
word in his thing

00:23:22.430 --> 00:23:27.340
was syllable itself, which is
multi-syllabic-- or whatever.

00:23:27.340 --> 00:23:30.950
So anyway, it was
